     Changelog.txt included in the pack.                                      
                                                                               
     Stardew Valley is an open-ended country-life RPG!                        
                                                                               
     You've inherited your grandfather's old farm plot in Stardew              
     Valley. Armed with hand-me-down tools and a few coins, you set out        
     to begin your new life. Can you learn to live off the land and turn      
     these overgrown fields into a thriving home? It won't be easy. Ever      
     since Joja Corporation came to town, the old ways of life have all        
     but disappeared. The community center, once the town's most vibrant      
     hub of activity, now lies in shambles. But the valley seems full of      
     opportunity. With a little dedication, you might just be the one to      
     restore Stardew Valley to greatness!                                      
                                                                               
                                                                               
     ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~                                                  
                                                                               
                                                                               
     1. Unzip & Unrar                                                          
     2. Run Setup.exe for install                                              
     3. Have Fun!!!
